Note by: Pablo Fernández Navarro
Date: 2001.10.27

You probably want to compile c2 with the option --disable-htmleditor
activated in ./configure so you are able to use the composer.

Note by: Pablo Fernández Navarro
Date: 23.6.2001

Cronos II path has changed, please, before executing c2 for first time create the directory
~/.c2 and ~/.c2/uidl (this will obviously be done automatically later).
